REPORT zrsa15_10.

DATA: gv_a TYPE i,
      gv_b LIKE gv_a,
      gv_r LIKE gv_a.

gv_a = 10.
gv_b = 20.

*Subroutine
PERFORM cal USING gv_a gv_b    "퍼폼은 ~~를 호출한다 라는 의미이다.(그렇다면 여기선 cal를 호출한다는의미.), USING gv_a=보내는변수
            CHANGING gv_r.

WRITE gv_r.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form cal
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM cal USING VALUE(p_a)           "USING p_a=받는변수
               value(p_b)
         CHANGING value(p_r).

  p_r = p_a + p_b.
ENDFORM.
